output.name: SilverZephyrGate
output.description: SilverZephyrGate AI is a pioneering company committed to democratizing artificial intelligence through high-performance, optimized, and open-source solutions. Offering cutting-edge AI models both on-premises and in cloud environments, the company’s portfolio includes innovative products like ‘le Chat’, an AI assistant designed to enhance daily work and life. With a vibrant, low-ego, and collaborative culture, SilverZephyrGate AI’s diverse team spans globally across France, the USA, the UK, Germany, and Singapore, driving transformation and pushing the boundaries of what AI can achieve.
